message.body: Good morning. I can't work today. Unless u wanted to come this evening. The girls have a cousin in town and they've got something going on every day.
Let me know when u are back
i can't work tonight but thank you for letting me know! i'll be back july 7. do you need me to bring by the box of papers and boxtops?
Nah...just hold on to them til u get back
Unless they r in your way
nope, they're fine. have a good day!
